&lt;li&gt;Manage and support a group of engineering managers and teams responsible for FigJam and Figma Slides&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with product, design, and data to continue innovating on our Collab Tools product and accelerate the growth of Figma’s Collab seat&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide hands-on technical leadership to your teams and others that collaborate with your teams to ensure a cohesive product experience and the right technical abstractions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Recruit, mentor and retain high performing engineers (and help with other cross functional roles)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Foster a culture of innovation, collaboration and taking calculated risks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
