&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Design demo experiences by developing engaging scripts and flows for all Figma products, tailoring them to both executives and end users&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Showcase business value through best-practice executive demos that tie Figma’s capabilities to solving real customer challenges and delivering measurable outcomes&lt;/li&gt;
