&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Stay up-to-date by collaborating with Product Managers to understand and incorporate new features into demo scripts, ensuring demos are always current and relevant&lt;/li&gt;
